text: Martina Pracht (born 11 April 1964) is a Canadian equestrian. She competed in two events at the 1992 Summer Olympics. She is a daughter and a granddaughter of fellow Olympians, Eva Maria Pracht and Josef Neckermann, respectively. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Canada Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1987 Pan American Games Category:Equestrians at the 1999 Pan American Games Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Canada Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Canada Category:Sportspeople from Frankfurt Category:German emigrants to Canada
